  CHUAH CHOO CHIANG:   Playing the foursomes, Siddikur, tell us about the day.   
SIDDIKUR RAHMAN:   Well, it was a really great day for us, me and Anirban.   I was really excited to play with him, one of my best friends on the Tour.   So it was really great and we played really good golf, both of us.   We played really good golf today and we really enjoyed, as well.   Really looking forward to tomorrow.   
CHUAH CHOO CHIANG:   Kiradech, your match with Thongchai, a halve with Miguel and Pablo, that was an exciting match.   
KIRADECH APHIBARNRAT:   We both did a good job today.   Thongchai was great.   We helped each other really well.   I made a couple putts, and when he missed we can get recovery.   But today it was great golf and a half point and happy with the result.   Hope we are up early on the first couple matches tomorrow.   
