HIDETO TANIHARA:     Same as yesterday.   We started out really slow.   We were behind the whole time yesterday, also today we were behind.   But we started playing better.   At one point we were down three and came back and we were up one.   We were looking for a win but they came back with a good birdie on 17.   But tomorrow, I think we'll have a good day tomorrow.   
   
